Package com.atakmap.android.routes

Class RouteGenerationTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<RouteGenerationPackage,​java.lang.Double,​RoutePointPackage>
      • com.atakmap.android.routes.RouteGenerationTask
  • public abstract class RouteGenerationTask
extends android.os.AsyncTask<RouteGenerationPackage,​java.lang.Double,​RoutePointPackage>
    Abstract class for generating routes. This class provides the basic infrastructure for registering event listeners in the form of RouteGenerationTask.RouteGenerationEventListener instances with its subclasses.
